com.gemalto.idp.mobile.otp.dsformatting.primitive

Interface DecimalInputDialogPrimitive

  • All Superinterfaces:
    InputPrimitive, Primitive

    public interface DecimalInputDialogPrimitive
extends InputPrimitive
    An interface representing a decimal input input dialog (DID) primitive.

    This primitive has type Primitive.PrimitiveType.DID.

    The allowed input format is InputPrimitive.InputFormat.DECIMAL_TWO_FRACTION_DIGITS.
